## API ENDPOINTS

### Authentication
```
POST /auth/google
  Request: { idToken: string }
  Response: { jwt, refreshToken, user }

POST /auth/refresh
  Request: { refreshToken: string }
  Response: { jwt, refreshToken? }

POST /auth/logout
  Request: { refreshToken: string }
  Response: { success: true }
```

### User
```
GET /user/status
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Response: { user, trial, subscription, usage }
```

### Submissions
```
POST /submissions
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Request: { url, platform }
  Response: { id, isDuplicate } | { isDuplicate, submittedAt }

GET /submissions
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Query: ?limit=20&offset=0
  Response: { submissions, total }

GET /submissions/check
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Query: ?url=<encoded>
  Response: { isDuplicate, submittedAt? }
```

### Custom Fields
```
GET /fields
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Response: { fields: Record<string, string> }

PUT /fields
  Auth: Bearer JWT
  Request: { fields: Record<string, string> }
  Response: { fields, updatedAt }
```

### Webhooks
```
POST /webhooks/lemonsqueezy
  Headers: X-Signature
  Body: Lemon Squeezy event payload
  Response: { received: true }
```

